href="http://www.english.upenn.edu/~jlynch/Courses/95c/Texts/louisa.html">Louisa</a>
in the <i>London Journal</i>.

</ul>


Search for "Johnson" in my experimental <a 
href="http://newarkwww.rutgers.edu/cgi-jlynch/chron.cgi?query=johnson">Eighteenth-Century 
Chronology</a> (it will also turn up Esther and Joseph Johnson)

